import React from "react";
import { Text, View, StyleSheet, TouchableOpacity } from "react-native";
import './alarm.css';

const Alarm = () => { 
    
    const selectMenu = document.querySelectorAll('select');

    for(let i = 12;i > 0; i--){
        i = i < 10 ? '0' + i : i;
        let option = `<option value="${i}">${i}</option>`;
        selectMenu[0].firstElementChild.insertAdjacentHTML('afterbegin',option);

    }
  return (
      <View style={styles.wrapper}>
        <Text style={{color:'red'}}>Alarm</Text>
        <Text>4:20:30</Text>
        <View style={styles.content}>
            <View style={styles.column}>
                <select style={{outline:'none',border:'none',height:'53px',width:'100%',fontSize:'19px'}}>
                    <option value="Hour" selected hidden>Hour</option>
                    
                </select>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.column}>
            <View style={styles.Minute}>
            <select style={{outline:'none',border:'none',height:'53px',width:'100%',fontSize:'19px'}}>
                    <option value="Minute" selected hidden>Minute</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="02">01</option>
                    <option value="03">01</option>
                    <option value="04">01</option>
                    <option value="05">01</option>
                    <option value="06">01</option>
                    <option value="07">01</option>
                    <option value="08">01</option>
                    <option value="09">01</option>
                    <option value="10">01</option>
                    <option value="11">01</option>
                    <option value="12">01</option>
                    <option value="13">01</option>
                    <option value="14">01</option>
                    <option value="15">01</option>
                    <option value="16">01</option>
                    <option value="17">01</option>
                    <option value="18">01</option>
                    <option value="19">01</option>
                    <option value="20">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="01">01</option>
                    <option value="3">01</option>
                    <option value="38">01</option>
                    <option value="39">01</option>
                    <option value="40">01</option>
                    <option value="41">01</option>
                    <option value="42">01</option>
                    <option value="43">01</option>
                    <option value="44">01</option>
                    <option value="45">01</option>
                    <option value="46">01</option>
                    <option value="47">01</option>
                    <option value="48">01</option>
                    <option value="49">01</option>
                    <option value="50">01</option>
                    <option value="51">01</option>
                    <option value="52">01</option>
                    <option value="53">01</option>
                    <option value="54">01</option>
                    <option value="55">01</option>
                    <option value="56">01</option>
                    <option value="57">01</option>
                    <option value="58">01</option>
                    <option value="59">01</option>
                   
                </select>
            </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.column}>
            <View style={styles.Second}>
            <select style={{outline:'none',border:'none',height:'53px',width:'100%',fontSize:'19px'}}>
                    <option value="AM/PM" selected hidden>AM/PM</option>
                    
                </select>
            </View>
            </View>
        </View>
        <TouchableOpacity style={styles.button}>Set Alarm</TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    wrapper:{
        color:'flex',
        alignItems:'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        width:'440px',
        backgroundColor:'white',
        borderRadius:'10px',
        padding:'30px 30px 38px',
        flexDirection:'column',
    },
    column:{
        borderRadius:'5px',
        padding:'0 10px',
        border:'1px solid #999',
        width:'calc(100%/3 -5px)',

    },
    button:{
        width:'100%',
        border:'none',
        marginTop:'20px',
        fontSize:'20px',
        padding:'17px 0',
        borderRadius:'5px',
        backgroundColor:'#4a98f7',
        color:'#fff',
        cursor:'pointer',

    }

})
export default Alarm;
